chinese: 抵制不良游戏，拒绝盗版游戏。注意自我保护，谨防受骗上当.适度游戏益脑，沉迷游戏伤身。合理安排游戏，享受健康生活。
english: Boycott bad games, no pirated games. Pay attention to self protection, beware of being cheated. Moderate games benefit the brain, addicted to games hurt the body. Reasonable arrangement of games, enjoy a healthy life.
spanish: Boicotea los juegos malos, nada de juegos piratas. Presta atención a la autoprotección, ten cuidado con las trampas. Los juegos moderados benefician al cerebro, la adicción a los juegos perjudica al cuerpo. Ordena razonablemente los juegos, disfruta de una vida sana.
portuguese: Não jogue jogos ruins, não jogue jogos piratas. Preste atenção à autoproteção, cuidado para não ser enganado. Os jogos moderados beneficiam o cérebro, o vício em jogos prejudica o corpo. Organize os jogos de forma razoável e desfrute de uma vida saudável.
french: Boycottez les mauvais jeux, pas de jeux piratés. Veillez à vous protéger, méfiez-vous de la tromperie. Les jeux modérés sont bénéfiques pour le cerveau, la dépendance aux jeux est néfaste pour le corps. Une organisation raisonnable des jeux permet de mener une vie saine.
indonesian: Boikot game yang buruk, tidak ada game bajakan. Perhatikan perlindungan diri, waspadalah agar tidak ditipu. Game moderat bermanfaat bagi otak, kecanduan game melukai tubuh. Pengaturan permainan yang wajar, nikmati hidup sehat.
malay:
Bad games Boycott, no pirated games. Pay 
attention to self protection, beware of 
Being cheated. Moderate games benefit the 
Otak, ditambah untuk bermain dengan badan. 
Reasonable arrangement of games, enjoy a 
Kehidupan yang sihat.

chinese: 玩家开始游戏后，运动员将随机撞击2,3,4其中一列，将该整列变为万能符号，SMASHING WILD中不再触发ROLLING REELS

chinese:
1.在点球界面点选球门上的6个按钮，进行射门
2.点球大战每次只有一次射门机会
3.结果有三种：免费游戏的奖励翻倍，金币奖励，射门不中
4.点球大战结束后，进入10次免费游戏
english:
1. Tap the 6 buttons on the goal in the penalty shootout screen to shoot
2. Penalty shootout has only one chance to shoot each time
3. There are three kinds of results: doubling the reward of the free game, gold reward, and missing the goal
4. After the penalty shootout, enter 10 free games
spanish:
1. Toca los 6 botones de la portería en la pantalla de la tanda de penaltis para disparar
2. La tanda de penaltis sólo tiene una oportunidad para tirar cada vez
3. Hay tres tipos de resultados: duplicar la recompensa del juego libre, recompensa de oro y fallar el gol
4. Después de la tanda de penaltis, entra en 10 partidas gratis
portuguese:
1. toque nos 6 botões no gol na tela de disputa de pênaltis para chutar
2. A disputa de pênaltis tem apenas uma chance de chute a cada vez
3. Há três tipos de resultados: dobrar a recompensa do jogo grátis, recompensa de ouro e perder o gol
4. Após a disputa de pênaltis, entre em 10 jogos gratuitos.
french:
1. touchez les 6 boutons sur le but dans l'écran des tirs au but pour tirer
2. La séance de tirs au but n'offre qu'une seule chance de tirer à chaque fois.
3. Il y a trois types de résultats : doubler la récompense du jeu gratuit, la récompense en or, et rater le but.
4. Après la séance de tirs au but, entrez dans 10 parties gratuites.
indonesian:
1. Ketuk 6 tombol pada gawang di layar adu penalti untuk menembak
2. Adu penalti hanya memiliki satu kesempatan untuk menembak setiap kali
3. Ada tiga jenis hasil: menggandakan hadiah permainan gratis, hadiah emas, dan meleset dari gawang
4. Setelah adu penalti, masuk ke 10 permainan gratis
malay:
1. Tekan 6 butang pada tujuan dalam skrin tembakan hukuman untuk menembak
2. Penembakan hukuman hanya mempunyai satu peluang untuk menembak setiap kali
3. Terdapat tiga jenis hasil: gandakan hadiah permainan percuma, hadiah emas, dan hilang tujuan
4. Selepas penembakan hukuman, masukkan 10 permainan percuma

chinese: 进入迷你游戏后，当转动出现武士时，当前转动出的怪物会根据种类移动到斩杀路线上，同时增加斩杀奖金。每个武士图示会触发一次斩杀。武士将怪物全部斩杀或怪物数量过多会停止游戏，进行奖励结算。
english: Upon entering the minigame, when a samurai appears by rotation, the monsters currently rotating out will move to the decapitation route depending on the type, while increasing the decapitation bonus. Each Samurai icon will trigger one decapitation. Samurai will kill all monsters or too many monsters will stop the game for bonus settlement.
spanish: Al entrar en el minijuego, cuando aparezca un samurái por rotación, los monstruos que estén rotando en ese momento pasarán a la ruta de decapitación dependiendo del tipo, a la vez que aumentará la bonificación por decapitación. Cada icono de samurái desencadenará una decapitación. Samurai matará a todos los monstruos o demasiados monstruos detendrá el juego para la liquidación de bonificación.
portuguese: Ao entrar no minijogo, quando um samurai aparecer por rotação, os monstros que estiverem saindo da rotação passarão para a rota de decapitação, dependendo do tipo, aumentando o bônus de decapitação. Cada ícone de samurai acionará uma decapitação. O samurai matará todos os monstros ou um número excessivo de monstros interromperá o jogo para a liquidação do bônus.
french: En entrant dans le mini-jeu, lorsqu'un samouraï apparaît par rotation, les monstres en cours de rotation se déplacent vers la voie de décapitation en fonction du type, tout en augmentant le bonus de décapitation. Chaque icône de samouraï déclenche une décapitation. Les samouraïs tueront tous les monstres ou un trop grand nombre de monstres arrêtera le jeu pour le règlement du bonus.
indonesian: Saat memasuki minigame, ketika seorang samurai muncul melalui rotasi, monster yang sedang berputar akan pindah ke rute pemenggalan tergantung pada jenisnya, sambil meningkatkan bonus pemenggalan. Setiap ikon Samurai akan memicu satu pemenggalan kepala. Samurai akan membunuh semua monster atau terlalu banyak monster akan menghentikan permainan untuk mendapatkan bonus.
malay: Apabila memasuki permainan mini, apabila samurai muncul dengan putaran, raksasa yang sedang putar keluar akan bergerak ke laluan pemotongan bergantung pada jenis, sementara meningkatkan bonus pemotongan kepala. Setiap ikon Samurai akan memicu satu pemotongan kepala. Samurai akan membunuh semua raksasa atau terlalu banyak raksasa akan menghentikan permainan untuk penyelesaian bonus.
Hindi: Upon entering the minigame, when a samurai appears by rotation, the monsters currently rotating out will move to the decapitation route depending on the type, while increasing the decapitation bonus. Each Samurai icon will trigger one decapitation. Samurai will kill all monsters or too many monsters will stop the game for bonus settlement.
Bengali: Upon entering the minigame, when a samurai appears by rotation, the monsters currently rotating out will move to the decapitation route depending on the type, while increasing the decapitation bonus. Each Samurai icon will trigger one decapitation. Samurai will kill all monsters or too many monsters will stop the game for bonus settlement.
Telugu: Upon entering the minigame, when a samurai appears by rotation, the monsters currently rotating out will move to the decapitation route depending on the type, while increasing the decapitation bonus. Each Samurai icon will trigger one decapitation. Samurai will kill all monsters or too many monsters will stop the game for bonus settlement.

chinese: 地球受到火热的宇宙流星的围攻--是时候逃到月球上去了! 登上火箭前往月球，但要小心即将到来的威胁，否则你会在一团火焰中坠落！选择什么时候跳下安全地带，并获得奖励！选择什么时候跳到安全的地方，并获得回报!
english: Earth is under siege from fiery cosmic meteors - time to escape to the moon! Board the rocket for theride, but beware of the inbound threat or you'll crash out in a ball of flames! Choose when to jump off to safety and eoarn the rewaids!
spanish: La Tierra está siendo asediada por feroces meteoritos cósmicos: ¡es hora de escapar a la Luna! Embárcate en el cohete rumbo a la Luna, pero ten cuidado con la amenaza que se aproxima o te estrellarás en una bola de llamas. Escoge cuándo saltar a un lugar seguro y ¡gana los rewaids!
portuguese: A Terra está sendo sitiada por meteoros cósmicos ardentes - é hora de fugir para a Lua! Embarque no foguete rumo à Terra, mas cuidado com a ameaça que se aproxima ou você cairá em uma bola de chamas! Escolha quando pular para um lugar seguro e ganhe os prêmios!
french: La Terre est assiégée par des météores cosmiques brûlants - il est temps de s'échapper vers la Lune ! Embarquez dans la fusée pour le voyage, mais prenez garde à la menace qui se rapproche ou vous vous écraserez dans une boule de flammes ! Choisissez quand sauter en sécurité et gagnez les récompenses !

Ancaman ke dalam atau anda akan memukul bola 
Api! Pilih bila hendak melompat ke tempat yang selamat 
Dan eo arn ada AIDS!

chinese: 游戏的内容是在火箭爆炸前决定何时跳下火箭。按信息荧幕上的PLAY键进入游戏，投注阶段显示倒计时，显示下注的时间和下注开始的时间。如果设置了AUT0 COLLECT，BET金额将默认为最低的BET金额，直到改变为止。在飞行过程中点击COLLECT按钮将结束飞行中的赌注，并返回显示的赢钱金额。
english: The game is all about making the decision when to jump off the rocket before it explodes.Press PLAY on the info screen to enter the moin game.The betting phase displays a countdown showing the time remoining to place a bet far the nextround and when it will begin.One bet can be set for a game round using the BET selector up tp a maximum.AUTO COLLECT allows an auto-eject value to be set for a round. This then plays the round and if the specified MULTIPUER is reached by the rocket, the astronaut will be automatically ejected.If an AUT0 COLLECT is set, the BET amount will default to the lowest BET amount until changed.clicking the COLLECT button during flight will end the bet in flight and return the win amount shown.
spanish: El juego consiste en tomar la decisión de saltar del cohete antes de que explote.Pulse PLAY en la pantalla de información para entrar en el juego.La fase de apuestas muestra una cuenta atrás que indica el tiempo que falta para realizar una apuesta para la siguiente ronda y cuándo comenzará.Se puede establecer una apuesta para una ronda de juego utilizando el selector de APUESTA hasta un máximo.AUTO COBRAR permite establecer un valor de auto-expulsión para una ronda. Si se establece un AUTO COBRAR, el importe de la APUESTA será por defecto el importe de APUESTA más bajo hasta que se cambie.Al hacer clic en el botón COBRAR durante el vuelo finalizará la apuesta en vuelo y se devolverá el importe de ganancia mostrado.
portuguese: O jogo consiste em decidir quando pular do foguete antes que ele exploda.Pressione PLAY na tela de informações para entrar no jogo.A fase de apostas exibe uma contagem regressiva mostrando o tempo restante para fazer uma aposta para a próxima rodada e quando ela começará.Uma aposta pode ser definida para uma rodada do jogo usando o seletor de APOSTA até o máximo.AUTO COLLECT permite que um valor de ejeção automática seja definido para uma rodada. Se o MULTIPUER especificado for atingido pelo foguete, o astronauta será ejetado automaticamente. Se for definido um COLETAR AUT0, o valor da APOSTA será padronizado para o valor mais baixo da APOSTA até que seja alterado.
french: Le jeu consiste à prendre la décision de sauter de la fusée avant qu'elle n'explose.Appuyez sur PLAY sur l'écran d'information pour entrer dans le jeu.La phase de pari affiche un compte à rebours indiquant le temps restant pour placer un pari sur le prochain tour et le moment où il commencera.Un pari peut être fixé pour un tour de jeu en utilisant le sélecteur BET jusqu'à un maximum.AUTO COLLECT permet de fixer une valeur d'éjection automatique pour un tour.Cela joue alors le tour et si le MULTIPUER spécifié est atteint par la fusée, l'astronaute sera automatiquement éjecté. L'astronaute est alors éjecté automatiquement si la fusée atteint la valeur de MULTIPUER spécifiée.Si un AUT0 COLLECT est défini, le montant du BET est par défaut le plus bas jusqu'à ce qu'il soit modifié.En cliquant sur le bouton COLLECT pendant le vol, le pari est terminé en vol et le montant du gain affiché est restitué.
indonesian: Permainan ini adalah tentang membuat keputusan kapan harus melompat dari roket sebelum meledak, tekan MAINKAN di layar info untuk memasuki permainan moin, fase taruhan menampilkan hitungan mundur yang menunjukkan waktu yang tersisa untuk memasang taruhan di ronde berikutnya dan kapan akan dimulai, satu taruhan dapat diatur untuk satu ronde permainan menggunakan pemilih TARUHAN hingga maksimum, KUMPUL OTOMATIS memungkinkan nilai pengeluaran otomatis diatur untuk satu ronde. Ini kemudian memainkan putaran dan jika MULTIPUER yang ditentukan tercapai oleh roket, astronot akan secara otomatis dikeluarkan. Jika AUT0 COLLECT diatur, jumlah taruhan akan menjadi default ke jumlah taruhan terendah hingga diubah. mengklik tombol KUMPULKAN selama penerbangan akan mengakhiri taruhan dalam penerbangan dan mengembalikan jumlah kemenangan yang ditampilkan.
malay:
Permainan ini adalah untuk membuat keputusan 
Bilakah anda melompat dari roket 
Tekan butang main pada skrin maklumat 
Masukkan mo dalam permainan. Peringkat taruhan 
Tunjukkan undur ke masa paparan 
remo meletakkan abet jauh di pusingan seterusnya 
Bilakah ia akan bermula. Boleh bertaruh 
Untuk pusingan permainan menggunakan pemilih pertaruhan 
tpa maksimum. Koleksi automatik membolehkan auto- 
Pop nilai untuk ditetapkan adalah kira-kira. Ini kemudian 
Main pusingan ini jika dinyatakan 
Roket mencapai Doppler 
Angkasawan akan dikeluarkan secara automatik. Jika 
Koleksi automatik ditetapkan, jumlah pertaruhan akan 
Lalai adalah jumlah taruhan minimum sehingga 
Perubahan. Butang kumpul semasa klik 
Penerbangan akan menamatkan pertaruhan dalam penerbangan dan kembali 
Jumlah kemenangan yang ditunjukkan.

chinese: 如果在飞行过程中点击收集按钮，自动收集值将被取消。如果收集发生在火箭爆炸的同时，赢的金额将被授予。如果火箭爆炸，赌注无人认领，将不会被退回。
english: An auto COLLECT value will be cancelled when the COLLECT button is clicked during flight.lf an COLLECT happens ot the same time the rocket explodes, the win amount will be awarded.lf the rocket-explodes and the bet is unclaimed it will not be returned.lf the rocket explodes, the player list showing the wins for any sulviving astronauts isdisplayed before resuming the next betting phase.A history of the last twenty multiplier values reached by the rocket are shown in the top left ofthe screen.
spanish: Si el cohete explota y la apuesta no es reclamada, no será devuelta.Si el cohete explota, la lista de jugadores mostrará las ganancias de los astronautas supervivientes antes de reanudar la siguiente fase de apuestas.Un historial de los últimos veinte valores multiplicadores alcanzados por el cohete se muestra en la parte superior izquierda de la pantalla.
portuguese: Um valor de COLETA automática será cancelado quando o botão COLETA for clicado durante o voo. Se uma COLETA acontecer ao mesmo tempo em que o foguete explodir, o valor do prêmio será concedido. Se o foguete explodir e a aposta não for reivindicada, ela não será devolvida. Se o foguete explodir, a lista de jogadores que mostra os ganhos dos astronautas sobreviventes será exibida antes de retomar a próxima fase de apostas.
french: Si la fusée explose et que le pari n'est pas réclamé, il ne sera pas remboursé. Si la fusée explose, la liste des joueurs indiquant les gains des astronautes survivants est affichée avant de reprendre la phase de pari suivante. Un historique des vingt derniers multiplicateurs atteints par la fusée est affiché en haut à gauche de l'écran.
indonesian: Nilai KUMPUL otomatis akan dibatalkan ketika tombol KUMPUL diklik selama penerbangan. Jika KUMPUL terjadi pada saat yang sama saat roket meledak, jumlah kemenangan akan diberikan. Jika roket meledak dan taruhan tidak diklaim, taruhan tidak akan dikembalikan. Jika roket meledak, daftar pemain yang menunjukkan kemenangan untuk semua astronot yang masih hidup akan ditampilkan sebelum melanjutkan fase taruhan berikutnya.
malay:
Nilai yang dikumpulkan secara automatik akan dibatalkan jika 
Kumpulkan butang pada 
Koleksi kipas flight.l berbeza 
Masa letupan roket, jumlah kemenangan 
Jika roket meletup 
Betis tidak dituntut, ia tidak akan 
Jika roket meletup, pemain 
Papar senarai pemenang bagi mana-mana su lviv ing 
Angkasawan pulih 
Peringkat pertaruhan seterusnya. Sejarah peringkat terdahulu 
20 nilai pendaraban dicapai 
Roket dipaparkan pada 
Skrin.

chinese: 点击图示，打开锁定功能；你可以锁定并继续攻击目标。如果锁定设置被选中，它将自动锁定被选中的鱼进行自动射击；在自动锁定的过程中，点击鱼来切换锁定目标。如果所有的锁定设置都没有被选中，你需要点击鱼来锁定捕获。
english: Click the icon to open the lock function; you can lock and keep attacking thetarget. If the lock setting is checked, it will auto lock the checked fish for autoshooting; during the process of auto locking, click the fish to switch the locktarget. If all of the lock settings are unchecked, you need to click on the fish tolock the capture.
spanish: Haz clic en el icono para abrir la función de bloqueo; puedes bloquear y seguir atacando al objetivo. Si la configuración de bloqueo está marcada, se bloqueará automáticamente el pez marcado para el autodisparo; durante el proceso de bloqueo automático, haga clic en el pez para cambiar el objetivo de bloqueo. Si todas las opciones de bloqueo están desmarcadas, tendrás que hacer clic en el pez para bloquear la captura.
portuguese: Clique no ícone para abrir a função de bloqueio; você pode bloquear e continuar atacando o alvo. Se a configuração de travamento estiver marcada, o peixe marcado será travado automaticamente para o disparo automático; durante o processo de travamento automático, clique no peixe para mudar o alvo de travamento. Se todas as configurações de bloqueio estiverem desmarcadas, você precisará clicar no peixe para bloquear a captura.
french: Cliquez sur l'icône pour ouvrir la fonction de verrouillage ; vous pouvez verrouiller et continuer à attaquer la cible. Si le paramètre de verrouillage est coché, le poisson coché sera automatiquement verrouillé pour le tir automatique ; pendant le processus de verrouillage automatique, cliquez sur le poisson pour changer la cible de verrouillage. Si tous les paramètres de verrouillage ne sont pas cochés, vous devez cliquer sur le poisson pour verrouiller la capture.
indonesian: Klik ikon untuk membuka fungsi penguncian; Anda dapat mengunci dan terus menyerang target. Jika pengaturan kunci dicentang, maka ikan yang dicentang akan mengunci secara otomatis untuk pemotretan otomatis; selama proses penguncian otomatis, klik ikan untuk mengganti kunci target. Jika semua pengaturan kunci tidak dicentang, Anda perlu mengklik ikan untuk mengunci tangkapan.
malay: Klik ikon untuk membuka fungsi kunci; anda boleh kunci dan terus menyerang sasaran. Jika tetapan kunci disemak, ia akan kunci ikan yang disemak secara automatik untuk penembakan automatik; semasa proses penguncian automatik, klik ikan untuk tukar sasaran kunci. Jika semua tetapan kunci tidak disemak, anda perlu klik pada ikan untuk mengendalikan tangkapan.

If the lock setting is checked, it will auto lock the checked fish for autoshooting; during the process of auto locking, click the fish to switch the locktarget. If all of the lock settings are unchecked, you need to click on the fish tolock the capture.

chinese:
1.简介
龙虎斗，即以牌面大小来决定输赢的桌牌游戏。游戏使用八副扑克牌，不含小丑。每局洗牌后，龙和虎仅派出一张牌就可以定输赢。
2.游戏规则
每局龙和虎各派一张牌，玩家可投注龙、虎、和三种结果。如果买中则按照桌面开奖结果获得奖励。
1).开牌结果
牌面点数由A到K，A为最小，K为最大，点数大者获胜，牌面点数大小顺序为: K、Q、J、10、9、8、7、6、5、4、3、2、A，点数相同则为和。花色不计算大小。
2).下注限红
每局个人所有区域下注总和最大为{0}
每局个人可在龙区域下注总和最大为{1}
每局个人可在虎区域下注总和最大为{2}
每局个人可在和区域下注总和最大为{3}
3).赔付规则
每局获胜区域根据桌面的显示比例进行赔付。如果本局结果为和，则龙和虎区域的下注全额退回。
3.功能使用
1).下注设置
点击设置可调整下注档位。一共10个下注档位，只能选择其中5个，选择后确认，桌面会切换为当前选择的下注筹码。
2).续投设置
续投可选择普通续投或专业续投。普通续投点击可按照上一局投注选择自动下注；高级续投可设定续投次数，设定后会在每一局开始前按设定时的上一局投注自动下注；直到次数完成或金币不足。
english:
1.Introduction
Dragon vs. Tiger, a table card game in which the size of the cards is used to determine winner & loser. The game is played with eight decks of playing cards, without jokers. After shuffling the cards in each game, the Dragon and the Tiger only send out one card to determine the winner.
2.Game Rules
Each game, the Dragon and the Tiger each send one card, players can bet on the Dragon, Tiger, and Tie. If you win, you will be rewarded according to the table draw result.
1).Opening Result
The number of points on the card is from A to K, A is the smallest, K is the largest, the one with the largest number of points wins, the order of the number of points on the card is as follows: K, Q, J, 10, 9, 8, 7, 6, 5, 4, 3, 2, A. If the number of points is the same, then it is a draw. Suits are not counted for size.
2).Betting Limit Red
The total amount of bets that can be placed on all zones in a game is {0}.
The total amount of bets a person can place in the Dragon area in each game is {1}.
The total amount of bets an individual can place in the Tiger area in each game is maximized to {2}.
The total amount of bets a player can place in the Tie area in each game is {3}.
3).Payout Rules
The winning area of each game is paid out according to the percentage shown on the table. If the result of the game is Tie, the bets placed on the Dragon and Tiger areas will be refunded in full.
3.Function Use
1).Betting Settings
Click on Settings to adjust the betting slots. There are 10 betting slots in total, you can only choose 5 of them, after choosing and confirming, the desktop will switch to the currently selected betting chips.
2).Renewal Settings
You can choose normal or pro rebet. Ordinary rebet can be clicked in accordance with the previous game betting options for automatic betting; advanced rebet can be set to rebet the number of times, after the setting will be set before the start of each game according to the previous game betting automatic betting; until the number of times to complete or insufficient coins.

chinese:
1.简介
这是一个以双方手牌大小来决定输赢的桌牌游戏。游戏使用52张扑克牌，不含小丑。每局洗牌后，红方和黑方各派3张牌，根据三张牌组合的牌型和点数，花色决定胜负结果。
2.游戏规则
每局红方和黑方各派3张牌，玩家可投注红、黑、幸运一击三种结果。如果买中则按照桌面开奖结果获得奖励。
1).开牌结果
首先比较双方手牌的牌型
三条>同花顺>同花>顺子>对子>高牌。
高牌：三张牌无法组成任何的牌型。
对子：只有两张相同点数的牌。
顺子：花色不相同，但点数连续的牌。(A.K.Q最大；A.3.2最小；不含A.K.2)
同花：花色完全相同，但点数不连续的牌。(A.K.J最大；5.3.2最小)
同花顺：花色完全相同且点数连续的牌。(A.K.Q最大；A.3.2最小；不含A.K.2)
三条：三张相同点数的牌。(A.A.A最大；2.2.2最小)
如果牌型相同则比较牌型的点数大小：
点数：A>K>Q>J>10>9>8>7>6>5>4>3>2
顺子：A.K.Q>K.Q.J>Q.J.10>J.10.9>10.9.8>9.8.7>8.7.6>7.6.5>6.5.4>5.4.3>4.3.2>A.3.2.
如果点数相同则比较花色:
黑桃>爱心>梅花>方块
2).下注限红
每局个人所有区域下注总和最大为{0}
每局个人可在红区域下注总和最大为{1}
每局个人可在黑区域下注总和最大为{2}
每局个人可在幸运一击区域下注总和最大为{3}
3).赔付规则
每局获胜区域根据桌面的显示比例进行赔付。幸运一击只根据本局红和黑中的赢家手牌开奖。如果赢家手牌符合幸运一击区域上开奖牌型的一种，则本局下注幸运一击的玩家视为投注成功，根据对应牌型的显示比例进行赔付。
3.功能使用
1).下注设置
点击设置可调整下注档位。一共10个下注档位，只能选择其中5个，选择后确认，桌面会切换为当前选择的下注筹码。
2).续投设置
续投可选择普通续投或专业续投。普通续投点击可按照上一局投注选择自动下注；高级续投可设定续投次数，设定后会在每一局开始前按设定时的上一局投注自动下注；直到次数完成或金币不足。
english:
1. Introduction
This is a table card game where the size of both players' hands determines the winner. The game uses 52 playing cards, excluding the joker. After shuffling the cards in each game, the red side and the black side will each be dealt 3 cards, and the winner will be decided according to the combination of the three cards, the number of points, and the suit.
2. Game Rules
Each game the red side and black side each sent 3 cards, players can bet on red, black, Lucky Shot three kinds of results. Players can bet on Red, Black and Lucky Shot. If they win, they will be rewarded according to the table draw result.
1). Opening Result
First compare the suits of both hands
Three of a Kind > Straight Flush > Flush > Straight > Pair > High Card.
High Card: Three cards cannot form any kind of hand.
Pair: Only two cards with the same number of points.
Straight: Cards with different suits but consecutive points. (A.K.Q is the largest; A.3.2 is the smallest; without A.K.2)
Flush: A hand with exactly the same suit, but with non-consecutive points. (A.K.J is largest; 5.3.2 is smallest)
Straight Flush: A hand with identical suits and consecutive points. (A.K.Q is the largest; A.3.2 is the smallest; without A.K.2)
Three of a Kind: Three cards with the same number of points. (A.A.A is the largest; 2.2.2 is the smallest)
If the cards are the same then compare the point size of the cards:
Points : A>K>Q>J>10>9>8>7>6>5>4>3>2
Courses: A.K.Q>K.Q.J>Q.J.10>J.10.9>10.9.8>9.8.7>8.7.6>7.6.5>6.5.4>5.4.3>4.3.2>A.3.2.
If points are equal then compare suits:
Spades > Hearts > Clubs > Diamonds.
2). Red Limit
The maximum sum of all bets per hand is {0}.
The maximum sum of all bets a player can place in red is {1} per hand.
The maximum sum of bets an individual can place in the black area in a game is {2}.
The maximum sum of bets an individual can place in the Lucky Strike area per game is {3}.
3). Payout Rules
Each winning area pays out according to the percentage shown on the table. Lucky Shoot only pays out based on the winning hand in the red and black of the hand. If the winner's hand matches one of the drawing hands on the Lucky Shoot area, the player who bets on the Lucky Shoot in this game is considered to have placed a successful bet, and the payout is based on the percentage of the corresponding hand shown on the table.
3. Function Use
1). Betting Settings
Click Settings to adjust the betting level. There are a total of 10 betting positions, you can only choose 5 of them, after selecting and confirming, the desktop will be switched to the currently selected betting chips.
2). Renewal Setting
You can choose either Normal Renewal or Professional Renewal. Normal Renewal can be set to automatically place bets according to the previous game; Advanced Renewal can be set for a certain number of times, and will automatically place bets according to the previous game before the start of each game until the number of times is completed or until the amount of coins is insufficient.

Each winning area pays out according to the percentage shown on the table. Lucky Shoot only pays out based on the winning hand in the red and black of the hand. If the winner's hand matches one of the drawing hands on the Lucky Shoot area, the player who bets on the Lucky Shoot in this game is considered to have placed a successful bet, and the payout is based on the percentage of the corresponding hand shown on the table.

1). Betting Settings
Click Settings to adjust the betting level. There are a total of 10 betting positions, you can only choose 5 of them, after selecting and confirming, the desktop will be switched to the currently selected betting chips.

You can choose either Normal Renewal or Professional Renewal. Normal Renewal can be set to automatically place bets according to the previous game; Advanced Renewal can be set for a certain number of times, and will automatically place bets according to the previous game before the start of each game until the number of times is completed or until the amount of coins is insufficient.
